  "tips": [
    {"type": "lead", "text": "Hello, friend! This is your very first lesson. We are going to find two special keys for your two pointer fingers. They are called F and J, and they will be your cozy little homes."},
    {"type": "drop", "text": "Rest your left pointer finger on F and your right pointer finger on J. Look! Both keys have a tiny bump you can feel. Those bumps help your fingers find their way home with your eyes closed, like a soft little path."},
    {"type": "callout", "icon": "🐱", "title": "Sleepy kittens", "text": "Let your hands rest soft and round, like sleepy kittens curled up for a nap. No need to look down, friend - just feel the bumps with the tips of your fingers."},
    {"type": "step", "kind": "placement", "target": "f j f j f j f j f j", "finger": "blue", "title": "Find your anchors", "hint": "Close your eyes and feel the bumps on F and J. Press them softly, back and forth, about ten times. Your fingers are saying hello to their new homes!"},
    {"type": "p", "text": "Did you feel them? Wonderful! Now we will tap F all by itself. Left pointer finger, press gently - it will find the key. After each letter, a little tap of the space bar with your thumb."},
    {"type": "step", "kind": "drill", "unit": "f", "baseReps": 12, "keys": ["f"], "target": "f f f f f f f f f f f f", "finger": "blue", "title": "Letter F", "hint": "Left pointer finger taps F. Press gently, friend! Your finger will find it."},
    {"type": "step", "kind": "drill", "unit": "j", "baseReps": 12, "keys": ["j"], "target": "j j j j j j j j j j j j", "finger": "indigo", "title": "Letter J", "hint": "Right pointer finger taps J. Soft and easy - feel the little bump."},
    {"type": "p", "text": "You found both your homes! Such a good job. When you are ready, press the button below and try the whole lesson. Take your time - you are already doing great, champ!"}
